135
00:11:56,480 --> 00:11:58,360
Can you please stop bothering me?

136
00:11:58,520 --> 00:12:00,400
Princess!

137
00:12:01,000 --> 00:12:02,640
Princess! Stop!

138
00:12:05,240 --> 00:12:06,480
Who is that?

139
00:12:07,640 --> 00:12:09,360
Your Highness.

140
00:12:09,680 --> 00:12:12,280
Elder son of Prince Qing He
and Princess Zhao Yun.

141
00:12:12,440 --> 00:12:15,600
You should know, Princess Zhao Yun
grew up without parents.

142
00:12:15,760 --> 00:12:16,920
She has no siblings either.

143
00:12:17,040 --> 00:12:19,560
So she is living with her uncle
for the time being.

144
00:12:20,200 --> 00:12:21,680
