151
00:12:39,720 --> 00:12:41,880
But he never attends
events like this.

152
00:12:42,040 --> 00:12:43,400
You are not going to see him.

153
00:12:47,960 --> 00:12:49,560
How dare you push me!

154
00:12:49,800 --> 00:12:51,000
Stop right there!

155
00:12:52,240 --> 00:12:53,680
Sister, save me!

156
00:12:54,360 --> 00:12:56,960
You Highness, this is
Princess Rong Le from Qi.

157
00:12:57,160 --> 00:12:58,360
Scram!

158
00:12:59,360 --> 00:13:00,520
I thought who is here.

159
00:13:00,680 --> 00:13:02,920
