to show your hideous look!

170
00:13:40,080 --> 00:13:42,480
Nicely done, Princess Rong Le!
He deserved this!

171
00:13:52,000 --> 00:13:53,760
Brother Wu You, you are here.

172
00:14:07,480 --> 00:14:08,800
Prince Li?

173
00:14:09,800 --> 00:14:11,200
What did you say just now?

174
00:14:12,240 --> 00:14:13,640
Nothing, I said nothing.

175
00:14:15,680 --> 00:14:16,800
I said...

176
00:14:17,000 --> 00:14:18,920
if Prince Li doesn't like this woman,

177
00:14:19,040 --> 00:14:21,000
I would never marry her.

178
00:14:22,360 --> 00:14:23,920
If this is the woman my brother likes,

179
00:14:24,080 --> 00:14:26,080
-you would marry her?
-No!

180
00:14:26,200 --> 00:14:28,800
