181
00:14:29,160 --> 00:14:32,560
I won't marry her whether
Prince Li likes her or not.

182
00:14:33,000 --> 00:14:34,640
You might as well be an eunuch then.

183
00:14:34,800 --> 00:14:37,280
No!

184
00:14:39,120 --> 00:14:40,200
Get lost.

185
00:14:40,320 --> 00:14:42,520
-Guards, take him away.
-Yes.

186
00:14:43,800 --> 00:14:45,160
