187
00:14:45,280 --> 00:14:47,400
-Get up!
-You can't take me by force!

188
00:14:47,560 --> 00:14:49,760
-You can't do this to me!
-Prince Qing He got a son at old age.

189
00:14:49,880 --> 00:14:51,040
He spoils his son a lot.

190
00:14:51,160 --> 00:14:53,280
-Let go of me!
-He lets him do anything.

191
00:14:53,560 --> 00:14:54,960
