Prince Li never does.</i>

203
00:15:22,480 --> 00:15:23,600
<i>He never drinks.</i>

204
00:15:23,760 --> 00:15:25,800
<i>He never touches a woman.</i>

205
00:15:27,000 --> 00:15:29,000
