some interest in me.

210
00:15:43,640 --> 00:15:46,360
Why don't you come
to the ball with me?

211
00:15:46,800 --> 00:15:49,280
The Empress arrives!

212
00:15:55,800 --> 00:15:57,840
All hail the Her Majesty.

213
00:15:57,960 --> 00:16:00,200
At ease, all of you.

214
00:16:00,680 --> 00:16:02,560
-Thank you, Your Majesty.
-Thank you, Mother.

215
00:16:05,360 --> 00:16:09,040
