218
00:16:15,320 --> 00:16:16,640
Prince Li is here.

219
00:16:16,800 --> 00:16:19,000
Come to the ball before you leave.

220
00:16:19,440 --> 00:16:20,680
Coincidently,

221
00:16:21,120 --> 00:16:23,800
Ya Li is here in the with us today.

222
00:16:24,320 --> 00:16:26,080
I am the daughter of
the Central Secretary, Ya Li.

223
00:16:26,240 --> 00:16:27,800
Greetings, Princess of Qi,

224
00:16:28,200 --> 00:16:31,080
Prince Li, Prince Chen
and Princess Zhao Yun.

225
00:16:40,840 --> 00:16:42,480
